OL,6,     FWhile 70s fever hits the Wetherby
OL,7,     Fpractice, Peter attends to a
OL,8,     Fgrumpy goose called Jemima, who
OL,9,     Fhas a nasty eye infection, while
OL,10,     Fold Collie Stomp needs life-saving
OL,11,     Fsurgery.
